{"tid":2398413,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門帝御．嵐天加推112伙　開放式折實售330萬起","createTime":"2021-02-07T09:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T06:49:07.000Z","uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ee21725075cd8958f20e047e8730c4840ad4e30f","tid":2398413,"uid":101341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T09:19:32.000Z","msg":"香港小輪（0050）及帝國集團旗下屯門「帝御」系列第三期帝御．嵐天，昨（6日）首輪開售，合共售出243伙，佔可供銷售之單位逾86%，總成交金額逾10.78億元，項目今日再加推5號價單，涉及112伙。<br />\n<br />\n負責銷售的恒地（012）營業（一）部總經理林達民指，該112伙單位實用面積由192至357平方呎不等，涵蓋20伙開放式單位、41伙一房單位，以及51伙一房半單位。當中，最低售價一伙為第7座3樓11室，屬開放式，實用面積213平方呎，折實售價329.96萬元起。"},{"pid":"d7ea0bc33814ed9e5fc73a22ea91dff044108156","tid":2398413,"uid":137725,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T09:27:15.000Z","msg":"1梯10000伙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母戇鳩鳩<br />\n<br />\n新私樓=On79 loser"},{"pid":"ec5f5878bb02c185ce5d8e117fbfaa4069d1c92c","tid":2398413,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T09:32:52.000Z","msg":"折實售價329.96萬元起<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f41e51fbd629a998943bf03dec3c41776369f42f","tid":2398413,"uid":267488,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T13:17:38.000Z","msg":"51伙一房半單位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"097f31aa2bde672f6613d7f2ea5bff2015571ff4","tid":2398413,"uid":2300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T13:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘩...上車了，好成功"},{"pid":"ac04bc5c049519e2869f69ea14e6b7ee5935ff7c","tid":2398